Searching the empty house it was clear that the occupants had rigged up a great many booby traps to catch transpassers, these could easily be of use to us as weapons or ammunition. However, a different prize presented itself in the basement. The former occupants had evidently met there end here amoung an enormous writhing colony of rats. 

 As I explained how so many rats could provide a tremdous amount of Dark Energy for me if we could subdue them, Andy began eyeing the various booby-traps.[PAGE BREAK] [BUTTON](Scenario_PreAlpha_FortifiedHouse_A_A){We decided to lure the rats into the booby-traps.} 

 [BUTTON](Scenario_PreAlpha_FortifiedHouse_A_B){We chose to ignore the rats and went about disassembling the booby traps.}
